structure.unit: B HOUSING, BUILDINGS, AND CONSTRUCTION - BUILDING CODE

law.history: Repealed 2008 Ky. Acts ch. 100, sec 12, effective July 15, 2008; and amended 2008 Ky. Acts ch. 100, sec. 8, effective July 15, 2008. -- Created 2004 Ky. Acts ch. 109, sec. 19, effective July 13, 2004.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/2008). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2008 Ky. Acts ch. 100, sec. 12, prevails over its amendment in 2008 Ky. Acts ch. 100, sec. 8.
